<paragraph blockId="24.[151,1436,1411,1510]" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,225,1411,1437]" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">Notes.</emphasis>
Reported from: North 
<collectingRegion box="[483,543,1411,1437]" country="Austria" name="Tirol" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">Tyrol</collectingRegion>
(NT) and 
<collectingRegion box="[660,779,1411,1437]" country="Austria" name="Vorarlberg" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">Vorarlberg</collectingRegion>
(VB). 
<bibRefCitation author="Szilady, Z." box="[858,1081,1411,1438]" pageId="24" pageNumber="175" pagination="624 - 626" refId="ref23040" refString="Szilady, Z. (1942) Neue Dipteren aus Bayern, Tirol und Vorarlberg. Mitteilungen der Munchner Entomologischen Gesellschaft, 32, 624 - 626." type="journal article" year="1942">Szilády (1942: 624)</bibRefCitation>
described this species and published records from North 
<collectingRegion box="[453,513,1447,1473]" country="Austria" name="Tirol" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">Tyrol</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion box="[570,693,1447,1473]" country="Austria" name="Vorarlberg" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">Vorarlberg</collectingRegion>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Aistleitner, E. &amp; Pruner, S. &amp; Schwendinger, G." box="[703,970,1447,1474]" pageId="24" pageNumber="175" pagination="137 - 163" refId="ref18356" refString="Aistleitner, E., Pruner, S. &amp; Schwendinger, G. (2020) Eine kommentierte Lister der Schwebfliegen (Diptera: Syrphidae) Vorarlbergs (Austria occ.). Beitrage zur Entomofaunistik, 21, 137 - 163." type="journal article" year="2020">
Aistleitner 
<emphasis box="[830,880,1447,1473]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">et al</emphasis>
. (2020)
</bibRefCitation>
recently reported this species for 
<collectingRegion country="Austria" name="Vorarlberg" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">Vorarlberg</collectingRegion>
. Nevertheless, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Szilady" authorityYear="1942" box="[373,502,1483,1510]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Melanostoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="175" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alpinum">
<emphasis box="[373,396,1484,1509]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">M</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[410,502,1483,1509]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">alpinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is excluded from the checklist, as this species identity remains unresolved.
</paragraph>
